remarks.format: ## Remarks 在內部處理所有的同步處理。 handles all synchronization internally. 如果兩個執行緒呼叫精確地說相同的時間點，在沒有作業遭到封鎖。If two threads call at precisely the same moment, neither operation is blocked. 兩個執行緒之間偵測到衝突時，每個執行緒都要再試一次擷取下一個項目，並同步處理在內部處理。When a conflict is detected between two threads, one thread has to try again to retrieve the next element, and the synchronization is handled internally. 嘗試從佇列中移除項目。 tries to remove an element from the queue. 如果方法是成功移除項目，則方法會傳回`true`; 否則它會傳回`false`。If the method is successful, the item is removed and the method returns `true`; otherwise, it returns `false`. 發生這種情況以不可分割方式相對於在佇列上的其他作業。That happens atomically with respect to other operations on the queue. 如果佇列已填入程式碼這類`q.Enqueue("a"); q.Enqueue("b"); q.Enqueue("c");`和兩個執行緒同時嘗試清除佇列項目，一個執行緒將會清除佇列`a`及其他執行緒會從佇列中清除`b`。If the queue was populated with code such as `q.Enqueue("a"); q.Enqueue("b"); q.Enqueue("c");` and two threads concurrently try to dequeue an element, one thread will dequeue `a` and the other thread will dequeue `b`. 這兩個呼叫會傳回`true`，因為兩者是無法清除佇列項目。Both calls to will return `true`, because they were both able to dequeue an element. 如果每個執行緒會回到清除佇列的其他項目，其中一個執行緒將會清除佇列`c`，並傳回`true`，而另一個執行緒會發現空的佇列，而且會傳回`false`。If each thread goes back to dequeue an additional element, one of the threads will dequeue `c` and return `true`, whereas the other thread will find the queue empty and will return `false`.
